snippet.title: Throwup Club ( Update 19 )
snippet.description:
Update 19 brings Throwup Club to Steam with its anticipated full proper artwork and glory! Along with the new art comes tons of new menu extras (such as the Character Gallery, and Music Player), dialog options, interactables, cutscenes, bucketloads of animations, and other features full of passion, love, and of course... vomit.

Collection 1 (Discs 0, 1, 2, and 4) will be available on Itch for $7, or on Steam for $9.99 with achievements. Those who own the current Disc 1 release on Itch will get this update, and the rest of the Discs in Collection 1 for free.

Collection 1 contains the following discs:
0 - Waking Up
1 - The Short Way Down
2 - Only As Evil As You
4 - The Spider's Web

Trailer Art Credits -
Sprite Art - @Catfan
Background Art & Music - @lolratz
